---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import { brand } from '../../config/brand';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Revenue Systems Consulting | UHL Systems" description="We design and build your complete revenue system. From strategy to execution - for online businesses that want to grow without more ad spend." />
		<style>
			.section-heading {
				font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px);
				line-height: 1.1;
				letter-spacing: -0.02em;
			}
			.hero-headline {
				font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 64px);
				line-height: 1.1;
				letter-spacing: -0.03em;
			}
			.cta-primary {
				background-color: var(--color-accent);
				color: var(--color-bg);
				border-radius: 999px;
				padding: 14px 36px;
				font-weight: 600;
				transition: all 0.2s;
			}
			.cta-primary:hover {
				box-shadow: 0 0 32px rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.35);
				color: var(--color-bg);
			}
			.cta-ghost {
				border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
				border-radius: 999px;
				padding: 14px 36px;
				color: var(--color-muted);
				transition: all 0.2s;
			}
			.cta-ghost:hover {
				border-color: var(--color-accent);
				color: var(--color-text);
			}
			.uhl-card {
				border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
				background: var(--color-bg2);
				border-radius: 16px;
				padding: 40px 32px;
				transition: all 0.3s;
			}
			.uhl-card:hover {
				border-color: rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.25);
				background: var(--color-bg3);
			}
			.content-width {
				max-width: 1100px;
				margin: 0 auto;
			}
			.prose-width {
				max-width: 720px;
				margin: 0 auto;
			}
		</style>
		<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
			"@context": "https://schema.org",
			"@type": "FAQPage",
			"mainEntity": [
				{
					"@type": "Question",
					"name": "How is consulting different from the Revenue Leak Audit?",
					"acceptedAnswer": {
						"@type": "Answer",
						"text": "The audit identifies what's broken. Consulting designs and builds the fix. In a consulting engagement, we go beyond diagnosis - we architect your complete revenue system, build the strategic playbook, and either guide or execute the implementation with you."
					}
				},
				{
					"@type": "Question",
					"name": "What does a typical engagement look like?",
					"acceptedAnswer": {
						"@type": "Answer",
						"text": "Engagements typically run 4–12 weeks depending on scope. It starts with a strategy sprint (audit + architecture design), followed by iterative implementation cycles. You get weekly check-ins, async support, and full documentation of every system we build."
					}
				},
				{
					"@type": "Question",
					"name": "Do you do the implementation or just the strategy?",
					"acceptedAnswer": {
						"@type": "Answer",
						"text": "Both. Our Method tier (3k - 6k) focuses on strategy and architecture with a detailed execution playbook your team can follow. Our System tier (7k - 20k) includes full hands-on implementation - we build, test, and optimize the revenue system with you."
					}
				},
				{
					"@type": "Question",
					"name": "What if I just need the audit first?",
					"acceptedAnswer": {
						"@type": "Answer",
						"text": "That's exactly what the Revenue Leak Audit is for. Start with the audit (1k - 2k), get clarity on your biggest leaks, and then decide if you want to engage us for the full consulting build. Many clients start with the audit and upgrade later."
					}
				}
			]
		})} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />

		<!-- Hero -->
		<section class="relative overflow-hidden px-6 py-24 md:py-36">
			<div class="content-width">
				<div class="prose-width">
					<p class="fade-in mb-6 font-mono text-sm tracking-widest text-accent uppercase">Revenue Systems Consulting</p>
					<h1 class="hero-headline fade-in fade-in-delay-1 font-display font-bold text-text">
						Architecture, Strategy & Execution
					</h1>
					<p class="fade-in fade-in-delay-2 mt-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted">
						Finding leaks is step one. Building the system that eliminates them - permanently - is where the real leverage lives. Revenue Systems Consulting is for businesses that don't just want a diagnosis. They want the cure.
					</p>
					<p class="fade-in fade-in-delay-2 mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted">
						We design and build your complete revenue architecture: the strategy, the funnels, the conversion systems, the monetization layers, the retention engines. Every component engineered to work together as one compounding machine - so you grow without throwing more money at ads.
					</p>
					<p class="fade-in fade-in-delay-2 mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted">
						Whether you need a strategic playbook your team can execute, or a full done-with-you build, we scale our involvement to match your needs. The goal is always the same: <em class="text-text">a revenue system that compounds.</em>
					</p>
					<div class="fade-in fade-in-delay-3 mt-10 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
						<a href={brand.strategyCall.checkoutUrl} class="cta-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2">
							Book Strategy Call - €97
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
						</a>
						<p class="mt-2 font-mono text-xs text-muted">30 Min | €97 | Payment at booking</p>
						<a href="/services/audit" class="cta-ghost inline-flex items-center gap-2">
							Start With the Audit
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<!-- Background grid effect -->
			<div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 40px 40px;"></div>
			<div class="pointer-events-none absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 -z-10 h-[800px] w-[800px] -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,255,136,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>
		</section>

		<!-- What We Build -->
		<section class="border-t border-border px-6 py-24">
			<div class="content-width">
				<p class="mb-4 text-center font-mono text-sm tracking-widest text-accent uppercase">The System</p>
				<h2 class="section-heading mb-6 text-center font-display font-bold text-text">
					What We Build
				</h2>
				<p class="mx-auto mb-16 max-w-2xl text-center text-muted">
					We don't optimize fragments. We architect complete revenue systems where every component reinforces the next.
				</p>

				<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
					<div class="uhl-card flex gap-5">
						<div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-bg3 text-accent">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 3H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-7"/><path d="M18.375 2.625a1 1 0 0 1 3 3l-9.013 9.014a2 2 0 0 1-.853.505l-2.873.84a.5.5 0 0 1-.62-.62l.84-2.873a2 2 0 0 1 .506-.852z"/></svg>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Revenue Architecture</h3>
							<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">The blueprint for your entire revenue system. We map every stage from acquisition to LTV, design the optimal flow, and specify exactly what needs to be built - and in what order. This is the strategic foundation everything else builds on.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="uhl-card flex gap-5">
						<div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-bg3 text-accent">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10 2v7.527a2 2 0 0 1-.211.896L4.72 20.55a1 1 0 0 0 .9 1.45h12.76a1 1 0 0 0 .9-1.45l-5.069-10.127A2 2 0 0 1 14 9.527V2"/><path d="M8.5 2h7"/></svg>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Conversion Funnels</h3>
							<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">We design and build high-converting funnels tailored to your audience and offer. Not templates - custom architectures based on your specific buyer psychology, objections, and decision-making patterns.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="uhl-card flex gap-5">
						<div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-bg3 text-accent">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="2" y2="22"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Monetization Systems</h3>
							<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">Upsells, order bumps, backend offers, pricing strategy, value ladders - we build the layers that turn a one-time buyer into a high-LTV customer. Most businesses leave 30–50% of potential revenue untouched here.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="uhl-card flex gap-5">
						<div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-bg3 text-accent">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 18a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H9a2 2 0 0 0-2 2"/><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="2"/><line x1="8" x2="8" y1="2" y2="4"/><line x1="16" x2="16" y1="2" y2="4"/></svg>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Retention & LTV Engines</h3>
							<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">Acquisition is expensive. Retention is leverage. We build the systems that keep customers engaged, reduce churn, and compound lifetime value - email sequences, onboarding flows, loyalty mechanics, and re-engagement campaigns.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- What You Get -->
		<section class="border-t border-border px-6 py-24">
			<div class="content-width">
				<p class="mb-4 text-center font-mono text-sm tracking-widest text-accent uppercase">Deliverables</p>
				<h2 class="section-heading mb-6 text-center font-display font-bold text-text">
					What You Get
				</h2>
				<p class="mx-auto mb-16 max-w-2xl text-center text-muted">
					Depending on your tier, you receive a complete strategic package - or a fully built and optimized revenue system.
				</p>

				<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
					<div class="uhl-card text-center">
						<div class="mx-auto mb-5 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent/10 text-accent">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.5 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7.5L14.5 2z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Revenue Architecture Doc</h3>
						<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">Complete blueprint of your revenue system - every stage, every component, every connection. The single source of truth for your growth strategy.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="uhl-card text-center">
						<div class="mx-auto mb-5 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent/10 text-accent">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18"/><path d="M9 21V9"/></svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">90-Day Execution Playbook</h3>
						<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">Week-by-week implementation plan with priorities, milestones, KPIs, and expected revenue impact. No guesswork - just execute.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="uhl-card text-center">
						<div class="mx-auto mb-5 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent/10 text-accent">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 20h.01"/><path d="M7 20v-4"/><path d="M12 20v-8"/><path d="M17 20V8"/><path d="M22 4v16"/></svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">KPI Framework + Dashboards</h3>
						<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">Custom measurement system so you can track exactly which levers are moving revenue. Know what's working, what's not, and where to double down.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Who This Is For -->
		<section class="border-t border-border px-6 py-24">
			<div class="content-width">
				<div class="prose-width">
					<p class="mb-4 font-mono text-sm tracking-widest text-accent uppercase">Is This For You?</p>
					<h2 class="section-heading mb-10 font-display font-bold text-text">
						Who This Is For
					</h2>

					<div class="space-y-6">
						<div class="flex gap-4">
							<div class="mt-1 flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-accent">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="mb-1 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Established Online Businesses</h3>
								<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">You're doing revenue but growth has plateaued. You've been patching individual tactics without a cohesive system. You need someone to step back, see the full picture, and architect a system that scales.</p>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="flex gap-4">
							<div class="mt-1 flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-accent">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="mb-1 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Founders Ready to Scale</h3>
								<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">You've validated your offer and have product-market fit. Now you need the revenue infrastructure to scale without proportionally scaling costs. This is the engagement that builds that machine.</p>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="flex gap-4">
							<div class="mt-1 flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-accent">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="mb-1 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Teams Without a Revenue Strategist</h3>
								<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">You have developers, designers, marketers - but nobody whose job it is to think about the revenue system as a whole. We fill that gap with senior-level strategic thinking and hands-on execution.</p>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="flex gap-4">
							<div class="mt-1 flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-accent">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="mb-1 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Businesses Tired of Ad Dependency</h3>
								<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">If your growth plan is "spend more on ads," you don't have a system - you have a dependency. We build revenue systems that compound from existing traffic, so every dollar of ad spend works harder.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- The Process -->
		<section class="border-t border-border px-6 py-24">
			<div class="content-width">
				<p class="mb-4 text-center font-mono text-sm tracking-widest text-accent uppercase">How It Works</p>
				<h2 class="section-heading mb-6 text-center font-display font-bold text-text">
					The Process
				</h2>
				<p class="mx-auto mb-16 max-w-2xl text-center text-muted">
					From diagnosis to a fully operational revenue system. Timelines depend on scope, but the structure is always the same.
				</p>

				<div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-4">
					<div class="uhl-card relative">
						<span class="mb-4 block font-display text-4xl font-bold text-accent/30">01</span>
						<h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Discovery</h3>
						<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">
							30-minute strategy call (€97) to understand your business, goals, and current system. We determine scope, timeline, and the right engagement tier.
						</p>
						<p class="mt-3 font-mono text-xs tracking-wider text-muted-dark">WEEK 0 &middot; €97</p>
					</div>

					<div class="uhl-card relative">
						<span class="mb-4 block font-display text-4xl font-bold text-accent/30">02</span>
						<h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Audit & Architecture</h3>
						<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">
							Deep analysis of your current system plus architectural design of the target state. You see the gap between where you are and where you need to be.
						</p>
						<p class="mt-3 font-mono text-xs tracking-wider text-muted-dark">WEEK 1–2</p>
					</div>

					<div class="uhl-card relative">
						<span class="mb-4 block font-display text-4xl font-bold text-accent/30">03</span>
						<h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Build & Implement</h3>
						<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">
							Iterative implementation cycles. We build each component of the revenue system, test it, and optimize before moving to the next. Weekly check-ins keep everything on track.
						</p>
						<p class="mt-3 font-mono text-xs tracking-wider text-muted-dark">WEEK 3–10</p>
					</div>

					<div class="uhl-card relative">
						<span class="mb-4 block font-display text-4xl font-bold text-accent/30">04</span>
						<h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Optimize & Handoff</h3>
						<p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">
							Performance review, A/B test results, final optimizations, and complete documentation. Your system is live, measured, and ready to compound.
						</p>
						<p class="mt-3 font-mono text-xs tracking-wider text-muted-dark">WEEK 10–12</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Pricing Tiers -->
		<section class="border-t border-border px-6 py-24">
			<div class="content-width">
				<p class="mb-4 text-center font-mono text-sm tracking-widest text-accent uppercase">Investment</p>
				<h2 class="section-heading mb-6 text-center font-display font-bold text-text">
					Choose Your Level
				</h2>
				<p class="mx-auto mb-16 max-w-2xl text-center text-muted">
					Start with strategy, or go all-in on implementation. Both paths start with the same rigorous diagnostic.
				</p>

				<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
					<!-- Audit -->
					<div class="uhl-card group flex flex-col">
						<div class="mb-6">
							<div class="mb-1 flex items-center gap-2">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-accent"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/></svg>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text">The Audit</h3>
							</div>
							<p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-wider text-muted-dark uppercase">Revenue Leak Analysis</p>
						</div>
						<p class="mb-6 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">
							Start here. Complete diagnostic of your revenue system with prioritized leak map and action plan. Option to continue working together afterwards - no obligation.
						</p>
						<div class="mb-6 border-t border-border pt-6">
							<span class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-text">1k &ndash; 2k</span>
							<p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted-dark">One-time investment</p>
						</div>
						<ul class="mb-8 space-y-3 text-[15px] text-muted">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-accent"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
								Full Revenue Leak Analysis (90 min)
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-accent"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
								Revenue Leak Map (all 7 stages)
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-accent"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
								Prioritized Action Plan + Quick Win List
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
